 abundance variations cannot be reproduced within\nthe context of our current understanding of stellar evolution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Nov 2001 22:35:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 15 Feb 2002 18:04:56 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 21 Mar 2002 00:22:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
