 SuperKamiokande, will have\na strong chance of distinguishing or at least strongly favoring one of the\nSolar neutrino solutions provided by present data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Nov 2001 18:36:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 19 Apr 2002 19:36:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-17"}
